 with read -r, which does not expand variables, and appends to the chat log with echo \"$userinput\" >> $chatlog\n  * heed only does tail -f on the chat log\n  * scry only opens the chat log with less\n  * no one has execute permissions on the chat log\n\nif you find a security issue, please contact us\n\n## notes\n\nif your file system does not support setting append only permissions with\nchattr +a, install.sh will fail\n\nbunkchat should work on all standard linuces. not tested on bsd\n\nPowered by Forgejo Version: 1.21.7+0 Page: 135ms Template: 10ms\n\nEnglish\n\nBahasa Indonesia Deutsch English Espa\u00f1ol Fran\u00e7ais Italiano Latvie\u0161u Magyar\nnyelv Nederlands Polski Portugu\u00eas de Portugal Portugu\u00eas do Brasil Suomi\nSvenska T\u00fcrk\u00e7e \u010ce\u0161tina \u0395\u03bb\u03bb\u03b7\u03bd\u03b9\u03ba\u03ac \u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0441\u043a\u0438 \u0420\u0443\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0441\u044c\u043a\u0430 \u0641\u0627\u0631\u0633\u06cc \u0d2e\u0d32\u0d2f\u0d3e\u0d33\u0d02 \u65e5\u672c\u8a9e\n\u7b80\u4f53\u4e2d\u6587 \u7e41\u9ad4\u4e2d\u6587(\u53f0\u7063) \u7e41\u9ad4\u4e2d\u6587(\u9999\u6e2f) \ud55c\uad6d\uc5b4\n\nLicenses API\n\n", "frontpage": false}
